\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 1. Core Architectural Constraints\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Priority 1: Reliability:
\f1\b0  Theme generation 
\f0\b MUST
\f1\b0  be 100% successful across all categories. This is guaranteed by the strict separation of duties (Theme Generator is static, Automation Layer is live).\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Role Separation:
\f1\b0  The 
\f0\b WP Generator
\f1\b0  component 
\f0\b ONLY
\f1\b0  creates static files (
\f2\fs26 theme.json
\f1\fs24 , patterns, templates). It 
\f0\b NEVER
\f1\b0  performs live WordPress actions (page creation, menu linking).\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Source of Truth:
\f1\b0  All color data must be sourced from the 
\f0\b Brand Kit Object (BKO)
\f1\b0 , which uses fixed slugs (
\f2\fs26 primary
\f1\fs24 , 
\f2\fs26 accent
\f1\fs24 , 
\f2\fs26 foreground
\f1\fs24 , etc.).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

