\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Data Ingestion:
\f1\b0  Parse user input, validate AI Content, map 
\f2\fs26 paletteSlug
\f1\fs24  to HEX values (using BKO).\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Configuration:
\f1\b0  Build 
